From: Sumit Garg <sumit.garg@linaro.org>
Date: Wed, 16 Oct 2019 10:44:53 +0530
Subject: KEYS: Use common tpm_buf for trusted and asymmetric keys
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
Git-commit: c6f61e59760df04a245ef48c8805b4eb3d958230
